channel.title: Proximity pkz [633 models + 602 anim + 602 gfx]
channel.description:
FOR ALL YOU HATERS THINKING I DIDN'T GET OWNER PERMISSION. [IMG]http://img140.imageshack.us/img140/460/mwsnap039.png[/img]
I'm Jake one of the Co-Owner's from proximity pkz. I'm here just to release the source + client. This server is now down. And won't be back up again. So here you go leechers. :)
ProximityPKZ is a 317 private server created by Alex, it features 602 animations and gfx client sided. Server sided it has a very good and correct combat fomula, curses, 100% working weapons, unique achievement system, vote system, and more!
Instead of just being a regular spawn, master, pure type pk server, you must earn your way to the top from getting kills. When you kill a player you’ll receive “Souls” with these souls you can use them to unlock new level sets which once you unlock you can switch to at any time. You’ll start off as a low level, and climb your way up the pinnacle of combat!
This is a few months old, closed the server after it slowly died out. Its a good pk server to start off with. Has some bugs which need fixing but all an all it runs quite well. The client has 633 models if I remember correctly, 602 anim, 602 gfx.
MEDIA! [IMG]http://i104.photobucket.com/albums/m193/mrgiggles1993/Untitled-8.gif[/img]
[IMG]http://i104.photobucket.com/albums/m193/mrgiggles1993/gmaul.gif[/img]
[IMG]http://i104.photobucket.com/albums/m193/mrgiggles1993/dds.gif[/img]
[IMG]http://img526.imageshack.us/img526/6814/83994040.png[/img]
[IMG]http://img842.imageshack.us/img842/476/loginbs.png[/img]
[IMG]http://img401.imageshack.us/img401/2324/previewwq.png[/img]
*Note, you might need to change the port plus remove the sql for both servers for them to run for you.
[size=36pt][font=comic sans ms]DOWNLOAD[/font][/size] CLICK[URL=http://www.mediafire.com/?d99lbw1ty5961jf] HERE[/URL] To download Proximity Pkz.
Old Video [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kE2QKc_BruQ[/youtube]
[font=impact][size=18pt]I'M NOT ASKING FOR REP OR ANYTHING LIKE THAT. JUST ANOTHER FAG RELEASING A DECENT PK SERVER SO ENJOY![/size][/font]
[size=18pt]CREDITS[/size] ALEX
